Hello?

01:42.058 --> 01:43.873
I'm sorry.
We're, we're, we're in...

01:48.670 --> 01:49.723
Hello?

01:50.331 --> 01:51.767
I'm sorry,
I can barely...

01:51.793 --> 01:53.587
We're, we're just...
we're, we're on a train,

01:53.614 --> 01:55.181
and I'm not sure if I...

